小姐到底是怎么度过这么多年的…"]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":356,"indent":1,"parameters":["BUST RIGHT FALSE"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["umi_lihui_test",6,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["其实以前用过不少啦，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["尤其是刚到地狱的时候，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["那时候我才十几岁嘛。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac突然传来的声音让我打了个激灵，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac然后我赶紧强迫自己把头压得更低了一些。"]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["umi_lihui_test",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["可惜你来得不是时候，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["已经过去那么久了啊…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac声音更靠近了一些，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac隐约中似乎多了一些幸灾乐祸的笑意。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：喂，抬抬头，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["我又不会吃了你。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac明明就吃过（虽然究竟是谁吃谁尚需疑问）"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我边想着边不争气地抬起了头。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"CG011",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":222,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":225,"indent":1,"parameters":[5,5,30,true]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":356,"indent":1,"parameters":["BUST LEFT FALSE"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["umi_lihui_test",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海、海猫小姐你在做什么？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：帮你找点配菜啊？"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,"CG012",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac纤细的手指搭在了我的裤裆上，让我下意识抿住了嘴。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：不过现在你是员工不是客人了，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["我可不会像之前那么遂你的愿了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：还是说其实你现在还不需要帮忙？"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"CG013",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[2]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac海猫抬起了头，红色的眼眸闯入视野和我对视着。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我的身体告诉我，自己没有说不的理由。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：今天只用手哦？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我僵硬地点了点头。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,"CG014",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：我可不是在征求你的意见哦？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac像被捏住后颈的鸭子一样，我的脑袋僵在原地。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac被压抑住的噗嗤笑声传来，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac很难想象我现在脸上是什么精彩的模样。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"CG015",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[2]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac拉链声传来，下身突然有种莫名的松弛感。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac下头轻松上头紧张，我考考你，这该怎么形容。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac这个世界颜色那么少，那精液会是什么颜色？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac如果一个人嘴上说不爱你，行为却好像爱你，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac那你应该看了几年动画片？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac纷乱的思绪占领了我的大脑，但下身却继续充血。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：很有精神地硬起来了啊…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac海猫的手正温柔地包裹着我身体的一部分、"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac上下地来回着。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：不过上次的时候，你可不只是下身强硬来着、"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["（那时候的我可是真正的无敌之人啊…"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["再不强硬可就要去下辈子了…）"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac没有理会我内心的自我辩白，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac海猫的手似乎报复性地加快了些速度。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：还说什么，如果没有我，就不会那么痛苦啥的。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac虽然嘴上说着抱怨的话，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac但海猫右手的撸动依然留有着分寸。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["我：对、对不起…我，我只是个失败的…"]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[30]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：噗嗤。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac你刚刚笑我了吧！明明就是笑我了吧！"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac不过我现在确实应该挺可笑的？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac不知道和刚到酒馆的我，哪个…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：不要再像上次那样说话了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac虽然依然保持着笑容，海猫的语气却突然严肃了起来，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac下身感受到的压力也变大了几分、"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac猝不及防下的我差点就要出丑了。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,"CG016",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：露出了很有趣的表情啊…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我确实已经几乎失去了表情管理，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac但不得不承认，海猫的脸对我来说本身就是最好的配菜。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac为了屏蔽快感不断寻找着转移注意力的目标，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac别说是我的脸，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我的大脑CPU可能都快烧起来了吧。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac但海猫已经把第二只手搭了上来。"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac两只手有节奏地上下撸动着。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac逃避没有用，红色的眼眸仿佛在对我说着。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我也确实无法从对视中逃离，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac像是已经被她困在层层网兜中已无力挣扎的猎物、"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac唯一能做的，就是不甘地睁大着眼睛。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"CG017",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[2]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac虽然话语停下了，但动作始终没有停下。"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac和言语的嘲笑不同，她的手一直保持着温柔和节奏感。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac啪叽啪叽，这声音是那么有节奏感，让人有些意乱情迷。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac一些液体的声音也逐渐汇入其中，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac是先走液吗？是这么叫的吗？还是叫什么…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac啪叽啪叽，新音效的加入是那么和谐、"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac让我的大脑仿佛也随着啪叽声被搅成了一滩浆糊。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac说不定其实她现在正当自己在打音游？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽啪叽"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac阿海唱歌不算很好，不知道音游技术怎么样？"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,"CG016",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac啪叽啪叽啪叽啪啪叽"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac话又说回来，这个海猫不是阿海啊，好像没法这么比？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac大脑努力地做着拉扯，但我不得不承认，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac确实这些天欲望已经累积过多了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac如果是平时，在这种临近极限的时候，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac我应该已经开始放慢节奏让自己缓缓了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac但现在的控制权并不掌握在我的手上，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac各种意义上…都不在我的手上。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["海猫：不是玩音游，只是单纯的服务而已。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac海猫进一步加快了手上的动作，"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\dac甚至开始试着根据我的表情调整刺激的部位。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",4,1,2]},{"code":401,"inden